Clare Thomas https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Clare_Thomas 0 Clare Lucy Thomas (born 2 April 1989 in Buckinghamshire, England) is a British actress who has appeared in several British films and television series. Some of her highest profile roles have been Aggie, one of the title character's classmates in the film Madeline, and Ingrid Dracula, daughter of the Count, in the children's television series Young Dracula. She also made an appearance in BBC One show Holby City, as the stepdaughter of a male patient.
